comments: Anthony (POR) catches the ball and holds it after the made basket, preventing the Jazz from inbounding the ball quickly.

Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in McCollum's (POR) path. After absorbing the initial contact from McCollum, Gobert re-establishes his screening position and he does not deliver any contact during the pick.
McCollum (POR) places two hands to Gobert's (UTA) front during the pick, but the contact is marginal when he disengages.
McCollum (POR) delivers contact to Ingles' (UTA) body as both players move around the pick. The contact affects Ingles' SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) turns and establishes himself in a legal screening position in McCollum's (POR) path when the contact occurs during the pick.
McCollum (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Ingles' (UTA) shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) briefly grasps Swanigan's (POR) jersey as both players attempt to retrieve the rebound. The contact is marginal.
After making contact with the ball, Lillard (POR) makes incidental contact to Gobert's (UTA) arm as he follows through during the rebound.
Swanigan (POR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Ingles' (UTA) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Ingles (UTA) reaches in and makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm that affects his SQBR prior to his gather and the start of his shooting motion.
Swanigan (POR) makes marginal contact to Bogdanovic's (UTA) arm during the drive that does not affect his ability to gather the ball.
Gobert (UTA) and Trent Jr. (POR) briefly engage and disengage during the pick.
Anthony (POR) makes marginal contact with Bogdanovic (UTA) off ball.
Anthony (POR) makes marginal contact with Gobert (UTA) as he moves towards the rim. Gobert's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Mitchell (UTA) and Trent Jr. (POR) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Swanigan (POR) makes marginal contact with Mitchell (UTA) after the release of the ball during his driving shot attempt.

Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) shot attempt after it hits the backboard and still has a chance to score.  Goaltending is only a reviewable matter when it is whistled on the floor by officials.
O'Neale (UTA) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Lillard (POR) during his driving shot attempt.
Swanigan (POR) makes marginal contact to Ingles' (UTA) body as he gathers the rebound.
Anthony (POR) briefly grasps Gobert's (UTA) shorts during the rebound. The contact is marginal.
Trent Jr. (POR) makes contact to Bogdanovic's (UTA) arm that affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
